\s Unachoka kwa matata na masikitiko?
\zon1 1
\zoli1 \bd Unachoka kwa matata na masikitiko\bd*\bd ?\bd*\bd  Yesu anaita\bd*\bd :\bd*\bd  \bd*\bd “\bd*\bd Kuja kupumzika.\bd*\bd ”\bd*
